Governor of Gombe state, Ibrahim Dankwambo has reached out to OBO, David Adeleke professionally known as Davido, to join him in getting Nigerian youths obtain their permanent Voters Card (PVC). Hello @iam_Davido. My name is Ibrahim Dankwambo, Governor of Gombe state. I’m a huge fan of your amazing work and talent. I’d be glad if you can use your massive influence to work together with me in convincing our young people to go get their #PVC.  Do I have your assurance?  However, Davido who seemed elated, replied the governor,"Anything to serve my Country and my  People Sir". 